        "subject": "LU-7814 utils: use -rc instead if \"errno\" as it may change",
        "message": "LU-7814 utils: use -rc instead if \"errno\" as it may change\n\nThis patch will replace strerror(errno) with strerror(-rc)\nin lustre_cfg.c. Sometimes errno may change intermittently\nand results in wrong error message to be displayed.\n\nSigned-off-by: vinayakswami hariharmath <vinayakswami.hariharmath@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: Ic890395878d98b00bcf33be6403fa40a93926216\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
